Jaws:



The great white shark took out his rifle shaped like a few foot long shark, 
walking towards where Prebon was, but could only see him on sensors, he 
wasn't even half way there yet.  He switched the weapon mode on his weapon to 
grenades.  No one was going to defeat the Alliance, especially the bases.
